You need to read up, study, know the game, know the mobs, the zones, your abilities, and your class. Alot of this knowledge is bought with virtual blood. This is why Ebay'ers, who do not know the game, are frowned upon. They didn't earn, and hence do not have, the knowledge to play their class.<br>
